229
00:11:59,534 --> 00:12:01,890
Don't worry, mi hija.
Santa has your list, too.

230
00:12:01,893 --> 00:12:05,400
And please, don't go snooping for
the gifts this year. He hates that.

231
00:12:05,403 --> 00:12:08,069
Santa can rip up my list for all I care.

232
00:12:08,072 --> 00:12:11,777
I mean, look at us, throwing
money away on bejeweled eggs

233
00:12:11,779 --> 00:12:13,946
like we're a family of Russian oligarchs

234
00:12:13,948 --> 00:12:15,347
when there are people in this town

235
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:16,875
who can't even pay
their own medical bills.

236
00:12:16,877 --> 00:12:18,710
And since when are you a communist?

237
00:12:18,713 --> 00:12:21,454
Since Archie told me that he and his dad

238
00:12:21,456 --> 00:12:23,522
are drowning in Fred's medical bills.

239
00:12:23,525 --> 00:12:26,575
To the tune of $86,000.

240
00:12:26,578 --> 00:12:28,361
Which is why I was thinking...

241
00:12:28,363 --> 00:12:30,497
- Absolutely not.
- Sweetheart, that's a lot of money.

242
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:33,637
The Lodge Charitable Trust has made
its donations for the fiscal year.

243
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:36,419
Fred Andrews will have
to tighten his belt.

244
00:12:36,422 --> 00:12:38,676
Said Ebenezer Scrooge.

245
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:41,574
Fred's selling Christmas
trees for extra cash, Dad.

246
00:12:41,584 --> 00:12:44,880
I mean, that's the kind of
man, the kind of father he is.

247
00:12:44,883 --> 00:12:46,282
You know,

248
00:12:48,049 --> 00:12:50,349
I believe I've some work
to finish in my study.

249
00:12:57,817 --> 00:13:01,061
Cheryl Marjorie Blossom,
what have you done?

250
00:13:01,064 --> 00:13:02,809
Isn't it obvious, Mother?

251
00:13:02,812 --> 00:13:04,630
I've saved Christmas.

252
00:13:05,659 --> 00:13:07,493
Look how happy Nana Rose is.

253
00:13:08,202 --> 00:13:11,003
You spoiled, wretched little brat,

254
00:13:11,005 --> 00:13:13,173
how do you expect to pay for all this?

255
00:13:13,176 --> 00:13:15,006
Oh.

256
00:13:15,009 --> 00:13:16,634
I was thinking

257
00:13:16,637 --> 00:13:19,678
